rulesList.cssText: .save-article-subscribe-prompt-flex { align-items: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; max-width: 660px; padding: 40px; text-align: center; }
.logo { align-items: center; display: flex; height: 30px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 16px; }

.prompt-header { color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font: 700 24px / 1.4 "Schnyder S", Merriweather, GeorgiaCustom; letter-spacing: -0.1px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px 16px; text-align: center; }

.benefit-text { color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font: 14px / 22px Graphik, Helvetica; text-align: left; }

.save-article-subscribe-prompt-link { align-items: center; background-color: rgb(220, 0, 0); border-radius: 8px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; font: 600 14px / 22px Graphik, Helvetica; height: 48px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 16px; text-decoration: none; width: 150px; }
